      <title>高盛、摩根士丹利、美国银行要求银行风险买家披露杠杆率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/goldman-morgan-stanley-bofa-scrutinize-srt-buyers-leverage</link>
